reviewText: This is an absolutely amazing deal great for Halloween! I got this specifically for Case 39 which is an awesome movie, and you still get two more good thrillers! The shipping was lightning fast i received this in less than a week! Definitely recommend! :)
I bought this pack for the Uninvited because it was cheaper to get all three of these movies than to buy it individually.  I had never seen Case 39, but it was good.  A great purchase.
this is the perfect scary movie 3 pack i have found.  my family enjoyed them, i hope yours does too..
I love horror movies however most that are made today are either ridiculously stupid or so boring, they put me to sleep. I love the fact that three of my favorite ones were in one pack.
